title: Pocahontas.2.1998.SWEDISH.DVDRip.XviD-EXTREM-E.avi
description: When news of John Smith&#039;s death reaches America, Pocahontas is devastated. She sets off to London with John Rolfe, to meet with the King of England on a diplomatic mission: to create peace and respect between the two great lands. However, Governor Ratcliffe is still around; he wants to return to Jamestown and take over, no matter what the cost. He will stop at nothing to discredit the young princess.
